Anglo American Platinum Unit Contributes $285 Million to Group, Anglo Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-25T06:02:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-25/anglo-american-platinum-unit-contributes-285-million-to-group-anglo-says.html
Anglo American Plc (AAL)  said its platinum
unit contributed $285 million to the company during the six
months to June 30.  The company commented in a stock exchange statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  